### ── PAYMENT SERVICE (/payments) ───────────────────────────────────────────
### Ortam: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Akış: createOrder (sales.http) → initiatePayment → capturePayment → refundPayment
### Admin/Manager: capturePayment, failPayment (PSP simülasyonu)

### 1. Ödemeyi başlat — Customer Bauer
### orderId: sales.http'deki createOrder'dan dönen ID
# @name initPayment
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/initiatePayment
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ORDER_ID",
  "provider": "StripeDE",
  "idempotencyKey": "pay-test-001",
  "amount": 38900.00,
  "currency": "EUR"
}

### 2. Aynı idempotencyKey ile tekrar — aynı session dönmeli (yeni kayıt oluşmaz)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/initiatePayment
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ORDER_ID",
  "provider": "StripeDE",
  "idempotencyKey": "pay-test-001",
  "amount": 38900.00,
  "currency": "EUR"
}

### 3. Ödemeyi yakala — Admin (PSP simülasyonu)
### paymentId: 1. adımdan dönen ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/capturePayment
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "BURAYA_PAYMENT_ID",
  "transactionReference": "TXN-STRIPE-001"
}

### 4. Ödeme durumunu sorgula — Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/getPaymentStatus(orderId='BURAYA_ORDER_ID')
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 5. Ödemeleri listele — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/Payments
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 6. İadeyi başlat — Admin (CAPTURED durumundan)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/refundPayment
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "BURAYA_PAYMENT_ID"
}

### 7. Ödemeyi başarısız say — Admin (yeni bir ödeme üzerinde)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/failPayment
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "BURAYA_PAYMENT_ID"
}

### 8. Başarısız ödemeden sonra yeniden dene — Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/retryPayment
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ORDER_ID",
  "idempotencyKey": "pay-test-002"
}

### 9. Başka müşterinin ödeme durumunu sorgu — reddedilmeli
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/getPaymentStatus(orderId='BURAYA_ORDER_ID')
Authorization: {{customerHoffmannAuth}}